# Sprint 003 — Impact Event System & Motion Intelligence

**Status**

Completed

**Period**

2026-06-30

---

# Sprint Goal

Increase the cinematic quality of generated videos by introducing intelligent editing events capable of controlling visual emphasis, pacing and motion throughout the rendering pipeline.

This sprint bridges the gap between AI planning and cinematic execution.

---

# Objectives

- Introduce the Impact Event System.
- Expand Motion Decision Intelligence.
- Improve cinematic pacing.
- Refine timeline execution.
- Increase rendering quality.

---

