# Architecture Decisions

This sprint introduced another important architectural layer.

### Event-driven Rendering

Rendering should react to structured cinematic events instead of static editing rules.

### Separation of Concerns

Timeline Planning

↓

Impact Events

↓

Rendering

Each stage now owns a clearly defined responsibility.

